WEBVTT

01:37.920 --> 01:41.020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.130 --> 01:43.970
[Episode 23]

01:52.780 --> 01:54.370
See? What did I tell you?

01:57.410 --> 01:58.340
Ming,

01:59.080 --> 02:00.340
what's wrong with you?

02:03.690 --> 02:04.690
Are you okay?

02:06.540 --> 02:07.720
He's choking.

02:08.070 --> 02:08.960
What's wrong?

02:09.020 --> 02:10.370
I think he's choking.

02:10.400 --> 02:11.420
Are you choking on food?

02:11.420 --> 02:11.910
Right?

02:12.810 --> 02:13.710
What should we do?

02:13.710 --> 02:14.520
Here, let me help.

02:14.520 --> 02:15.080
How are you?

02:15.080 --> 02:15.770
Get up.

02:15.820 --> 02:16.450
Slowly.

02:17.470 --> 02:18.840
-How are you?
-Let me help you.

02:18.840 --> 02:20.170
I'll help you get it out.

02:20.430 --> 02:21.810
Ready? One, two, three.

02:22.430 --> 02:25.360
One, two, three.

02:26.860 --> 02:28.100
How are you?

02:29.390 --> 02:30.430
Sit down first.

02:30.460 --> 02:32.100
Come on, slowly.

02:33.960 --> 02:35.570
You scared me to death.

02:36.770 --> 02:37.460
Just now,

02:38.579 --> 02:39.540
it felt like

02:41.290 --> 02:43.470
my whole life flashed before my eyes.

02:43.650 --> 02:44.530
A life flashback?

02:44.530 --> 02:45.560
You...

02:45.579 --> 02:47.610
You practically got
a second chance at life.

02:47.610 --> 02:48.400
Ming,

02:48.610 --> 02:49.340
are you okay?

02:49.460 --> 02:50.520
Are you okay or not?

02:50.710 --> 02:51.640
I'm fine.

02:52.170 --> 02:53.360
I'm fine now.

02:54.070 --> 02:55.110
Thank you,

02:55.410 --> 02:56.250
Mr. Ji.

02:56.280 --> 02:58.079
It's nothing. Glad you're okay.

02:58.460 --> 02:59.700
Are you really okay?

03:01.580 --> 03:02.370
Yes.

03:03.070 --> 03:03.980
Of course I am.

03:05.930 --> 03:07.950
I don't think you are.

03:08.190 --> 03:09.790
You'd better go to
the hospital for a checkup.

03:09.790 --> 03:11.770
You still need to go to the hospital
for a further checkup.

03:11.770 --> 03:13.380
You can't take this lightly.

03:13.770 --> 03:14.730
-I'll send him there.
-Come on.

03:14.730 --> 03:15.660
Come, slowly.

03:16.570 --> 03:17.130
Slowly.

03:17.420 --> 03:18.100
Let's go.

03:19.740 --> 03:20.360
Can you do it?

03:20.360 --> 03:20.980
Leave it to me.

03:20.980 --> 03:21.470
Okay.

03:23.150 --> 03:24.060
Wait for me.

03:24.360 --> 03:25.490
I'll be right back.

03:25.520 --> 03:26.610
-I'll wait for you.
-Be careful.

03:26.610 --> 03:28.010
Hurry up and get checked.

03:28.670 --> 03:29.630
It's not like we're playing mahjong—

03:29.630 --> 03:31.160
we're not waiting for a fourth player.

03:31.160 --> 03:32.150
What happened?

03:32.180 --> 03:33.310
The old man choked.

03:33.329 --> 03:34.170
I'm taking him to the hospital.

03:34.170 --> 03:35.030
Be careful on the way.

03:35.030 --> 03:35.380
Okay.

03:35.530 --> 03:36.310
Go quickly.

03:41.000 --> 03:43.290
Are there any other solutions?

03:43.630 --> 03:45.020
I'll make some calls to find someone.

03:45.020 --> 03:45.970
Now?

03:46.240 --> 03:47.550
It's too late for a last-minute effort.

03:47.550 --> 03:49.160
We haven't worked together before.

03:49.160 --> 03:50.320
How can we perform?

03:52.530 --> 03:54.790
Can the performance still go as planned?

03:55.120 --> 03:57.680
Ms. Xu, the guests are about to enter.

03:58.030 --> 03:58.750
Copy that.

04:00.050 --> 04:02.180
Take care of the guests outside first.

04:02.940 --> 04:04.340
What about the band?

04:05.210 --> 04:06.280
Leave the band

04:06.460 --> 04:07.300
to me.

04:07.980 --> 04:08.710
Don't worry.

04:09.480 --> 04:10.280
I've got this.

04:13.900 --> 04:16.380
[Lusia University 60th Anniversary]

04:29.810 --> 04:31.610
Hello. Please come in.

04:38.050 --> 04:39.330
Ms. Dianjiangchun.

04:41.310 --> 04:43.520
It's me. I heard your hotel

04:43.540 --> 04:45.300
has a jazz performance tonight.

04:45.300 --> 04:46.620
I just came to join the fun.

04:46.620 --> 04:47.800
Let me find you a seat.

04:47.800 --> 04:48.350
Follow me.

04:48.350 --> 04:48.950
Thank you.

04:58.330 --> 04:59.550
This is a good seat.

05:01.540 --> 05:02.600
Please have a seat.

05:07.070 --> 05:07.900
It's okay.

05:08.850 --> 05:09.440
Thank you.

05:09.440 --> 05:10.030
It's fine.

05:10.030 --> 05:11.490
Go do your work. Don't worry about me.

05:11.490 --> 05:13.290
Let me know if you need anything.

05:32.520 --> 05:33.409
Miyu.

05:34.620 --> 05:35.659
Chairman Wei.

05:36.260 --> 05:38.360
The decoration has quite a nice vibe.

05:39.080 --> 05:41.210
How did the rehearsal go this morning?

05:41.500 --> 05:44.330
Those old guys won't
sing out of tune, will they?

05:44.350 --> 05:45.350
They...

05:46.330 --> 05:47.180
They are here.

05:54.460 --> 05:56.000
Please take a seat here.

06:10.860 --> 06:18.060
[Lusia University 60th Anniversary]

06:22.370 --> 06:23.470
[Lusia University 60th Anniversary]

06:31.050 --> 06:34.460
[Lusia University 60th Anniversary]

09:14.900 --> 09:20.390
[Lusia University 60th Anniversary]

09:55.520 --> 09:57.390
Do you want to watch our performance too?

09:57.390 --> 09:58.550
Yes. Can we?

09:58.580 --> 09:59.450
Of course.

09:59.470 --> 10:00.040
Come.

10:00.110 --> 10:00.830
Thank you.

10:01.130 --> 10:02.130
This way, please.

10:05.850 --> 10:06.620
Sit here.

10:07.710 --> 10:09.050
You can stay here.

10:39.030 --> 10:40.790
Thank you, Mr. Ji,

10:40.790 --> 10:41.560
for saving us.

10:41.560 --> 10:43.090
Here's to our cooperation.

10:51.900 --> 10:52.790
Thank you.

10:55.000 --> 10:56.360
What does it say?

10:56.740 --> 10:57.790
Let's see.

11:01.780 --> 11:02.870
Ji Feng.

11:04.890 --> 11:05.910
Thank you.

11:21.160 --> 11:22.000
[A jazz performance by Shanghai's
old-school gentlemen]

11:22.020 --> 11:22.830
[Old Shanghai jazz performance]

11:22.850 --> 11:23.660
[Uncles' jazz music]

11:23.690 --> 11:24.800
[The most stylish in Shanghai]

11:26.210 --> 11:26.530
[Comments]

11:26.550 --> 11:27.210
[Where is this show?]

11:27.210 --> 11:27.570
[Everyone, this is the jazz performance
at Purong Hotel]

11:27.570 --> 11:27.800
[The guy in the white suit
playing saxophone is so handsome]

11:27.800 --> 11:28.390
[I didn't know jazz could sound this good]

11:28.390 --> 11:28.970
[Purong is amazing]

11:28.970 --> 11:29.360
[Ahhh, I'm here live—
the location is Purong Hotel]

11:29.380 --> 11:29.630
[Everyone, hurry and come!]

11:29.660 --> 11:30.240
[I'm so happy.]

11:30.240 --> 11:30.630
[It's nice.]

11:30.670 --> 11:31.710
[Purong Hotel jazz performance
recap is here]

11:31.770 --> 11:32.180
[A reunion after sixty years,
an unforgettable night]

11:32.240 --> 11:32.980
[Meiling's life]

11:33.000 --> 11:33.440
[Sort by popularity]

11:33.470 --> 11:33.730
[Come copy this idea together]

11:33.800 --> 11:34.940
[Purong Hotel's senior jazz performance
is going viral!]

11:43.260 --> 11:44.260
Take care.

11:44.730 --> 11:45.330
Okay.

11:45.410 --> 11:46.370
Goodbye.

11:46.710 --> 11:47.400
Goodbye.

11:47.510 --> 11:48.050
Goodbye.

11:48.080 --> 11:49.150
We will meet again.

11:49.150 --> 11:50.200
Definitely, we will meet again.

11:50.200 --> 11:50.630
Bye.

11:50.650 --> 11:51.080
Bye.

11:51.110 --> 11:51.750
Bye. Bye.

11:51.750 --> 11:52.600
Goodbye.

11:57.210 --> 11:58.250
Daniel,

11:59.090 --> 12:01.490
congratulations
on your successful performance.

12:01.490 --> 12:02.450
Thank you.

12:05.260 --> 12:08.850
This is just a beautiful dream.

12:11.320 --> 12:12.590
What a nice dream.

12:13.770 --> 12:14.810
It is a good dream.

12:15.400 --> 12:16.730
But wouldn't it be great

12:17.440 --> 12:19.440
if we could

12:21.090 --> 12:22.750
never wake up from this dream?

12:44.330 --> 12:46.130
Come to the Western restaurant.

12:46.850 --> 12:48.600
Although the reaction was good today,

12:48.600 --> 12:51.240
there are still many areas to improve.

12:51.660 --> 12:53.530
I saw everyone really
enjoyed your performance.

12:53.530 --> 12:55.190
Please give me more feedback.

12:55.350 --> 12:56.370
Mr. Ji, you were looking for me?

12:56.370 --> 12:56.980
Yes.

12:58.020 --> 12:59.880
Aren't you going to introduce us?

12:59.880 --> 13:02.240
This is our lobby manager, Xu Miyu,

13:02.440 --> 13:03.990
and she is also the person in charge

13:03.990 --> 13:05.320
of the concert tonight.

13:06.290 --> 13:07.020
This is...

13:07.050 --> 13:08.290
Ms. Dianjiangchun,

13:09.020 --> 13:10.550
I'm a big fan of yours.

13:11.010 --> 13:12.920
Really? Thank you for your attention.

13:12.920 --> 13:14.320
My name is Jiang Zhichun.

13:15.520 --> 13:17.720
Tonight's concert was really amazing.

13:18.120 --> 13:19.160
Especially since

13:19.300 --> 13:20.450
I didn't expect Mr. Ji

13:20.450 --> 13:21.880
to have such talent.

13:22.470 --> 13:24.950
Seriously, consider
appearing on my channel.

13:24.950 --> 13:26.310
I will definitely turn you into

13:26.310 --> 13:27.700
a superstar of the hotel industry.

13:27.700 --> 13:28.460
No,

13:28.480 --> 13:29.940
please don't joke with me.

13:30.640 --> 13:32.470
You guys can talk.

13:32.620 --> 13:33.500
We'll be in touch later.

13:33.500 --> 13:33.980
Okay.

13:34.400 --> 13:35.520
I'll walk you out.

13:35.550 --> 13:37.280
It's fine, you guys talk.

13:38.290 --> 13:39.420
Alright, take care.

13:44.300 --> 13:45.690
Have a seat.

13:52.670 --> 13:53.550
Try this.

14:06.930 --> 14:08.280
What do you think of this place?

14:08.280 --> 14:09.810
I want to hear your opinion.

14:11.300 --> 14:12.180
I think

14:12.920 --> 14:15.610
the equipment is pretty complete.

14:16.130 --> 14:17.050
But

14:17.390 --> 14:18.950
it lacks refinement.

14:19.120 --> 14:21.180
Take these snacks for example. Look,

14:21.280 --> 14:23.040
they're barely touched on the tables.

14:23.040 --> 14:24.440
An amateur setup, right?

14:24.640 --> 14:26.330
I didn't say that.

14:26.470 --> 14:28.020
I think you're absolutely right.

14:28.020 --> 14:29.290
We're on the same page.

14:29.990 --> 14:31.380
Next, I want to

14:31.810 --> 14:33.340
upgrade this amateur setup

14:34.120 --> 14:37.120
and make it a truly
high-class performance venue.

14:37.230 --> 14:38.230
What do you mean?

14:38.250 --> 14:39.780
Didn't you hear what I said?

14:40.450 --> 14:43.310
You want to continue the performances
in the Western restaurant?

14:43.310 --> 14:44.440
As you saw,

14:44.720 --> 14:46.170
tonight's performance

14:46.370 --> 14:48.250
actually had a really good response.

14:48.250 --> 14:49.580
So I decided

14:49.720 --> 14:51.320
that the next performance

14:51.600 --> 14:53.010
will be this Friday.

14:53.040 --> 14:54.490
If Daniel finds out,

14:54.520 --> 14:55.760
he'll be thrilled.

14:57.420 --> 14:59.270
But I have other considerations.

14:59.270 --> 15:00.320
Daniel's band

15:00.320 --> 15:02.030
has an average age of over 70.

15:02.320 --> 15:04.030
It's good. It's a selling point.

15:04.030 --> 15:05.830
But at the same time, it's a risk.

15:07.040 --> 15:07.970
Isn't this

15:08.230 --> 15:10.520
exactly the value of Mr. Ji?

15:11.710 --> 15:13.970
Health issues at an advanced age
are indeed a pain point,

15:13.970 --> 15:17.210
but if we manage the risks well,

15:17.360 --> 15:19.170
this pain point can also become

15:19.200 --> 15:21.200
a rare highlight and selling point.

15:21.230 --> 15:22.630
What do you think, Mr. Ji?

15:23.400 --> 15:25.400
You're leaving this question to me.

15:27.870 --> 15:30.140
So you were testing me.

15:31.030 --> 15:33.430
So what kind of answer
do you want to give me?

15:34.900 --> 15:36.240
Every close call without disaster

15:36.240 --> 15:37.810
helps us rise to the next level.

15:37.810 --> 15:38.580
So,

15:38.640 --> 15:41.090
I won't be scared off by a minor accident.

15:41.240 --> 15:43.430
After all, people always aim higher.

15:46.700 --> 15:47.500
Then,

15:48.030 --> 15:51.510
how about you and I share the risks

15:52.020 --> 15:52.900
together?

15:54.910 --> 15:56.320
I think the performances here

15:56.320 --> 15:57.790
can continue long-term,

15:58.070 --> 15:59.380
but on one condition—

15:59.410 --> 16:01.620
I want the person managing them

16:01.640 --> 16:02.430
to be you.

16:03.640 --> 16:04.480
Me?

16:04.920 --> 16:05.560
Yes.

16:06.800 --> 16:08.680
Really, I need you.

16:20.900 --> 16:21.530
[Party A: Purong Hotel Co., Ltd.]

16:21.550 --> 16:22.560
[Party B: Daniel and his friends' band]

16:24.630 --> 16:25.350
Really?

16:26.670 --> 16:27.150
Yes.

16:27.270 --> 16:28.010
Yes.

16:28.030 --> 16:28.880
Really.

16:29.440 --> 16:30.080
Really.

16:30.110 --> 16:31.020
Yes!

16:35.040 --> 16:36.570
You were right to come back.

17:11.339 --> 17:18.540
[Daniel and his friends]

17:19.349 --> 17:20.400
Attention, everyone.

17:20.400 --> 17:21.589
Starting today,

17:21.589 --> 17:24.040
Ms. Xu will not only be our lobby manager,

17:24.060 --> 17:26.380
but she will also work
at the jazz bar at night.

17:26.380 --> 17:27.609
So please be understanding.

17:27.609 --> 17:28.870
If you can solve a problem yourselves,

17:28.870 --> 17:30.670
don't always bother Ms. Xu.

17:30.800 --> 17:31.560
All right.

17:33.300 --> 17:34.130
Back to work.

17:38.200 --> 17:39.800
How impressive can she be?

17:39.990 --> 17:41.870
At work, she's juggling two jobs at once.

17:41.870 --> 17:43.800
Well, she's got powerful backing.

17:45.660 --> 17:50.780
[Purong Hotel]

17:49.300 --> 17:51.430
Lu Xiaoyan, make three copies of this.

18:50.160 --> 18:51.220
What are you doing?

18:51.220 --> 18:54.080
In broad daylight,
you're giving me a heart attack?

18:57.430 --> 18:58.280
Come up.

19:07.640 --> 19:10.360
Director Bai, ever since I joined Purong

19:10.390 --> 19:12.820
and the Front Office,
I've been working under you.

19:12.820 --> 19:15.390
You know how much overtime I've worked

19:15.420 --> 19:17.230
and how many all-nighters I've pulled.

19:17.230 --> 19:18.180
But what happened?

19:18.180 --> 19:20.030
Xu Miyu came out of nowhere,

19:20.590 --> 19:23.110
stole my lobby manager position.

19:23.130 --> 19:25.480
She's holding onto the jazz bar too.

19:25.680 --> 19:26.720
Why does Xu Miyu get

19:26.720 --> 19:28.400
all the benefits to herself?

19:28.400 --> 19:29.750
Why?

19:30.000 --> 19:32.270
You didn't say a single word for me.

19:33.320 --> 19:34.120
Don't cry.

19:35.680 --> 19:36.160
Alright.

19:36.160 --> 19:37.200
Stop crying.

19:37.290 --> 19:39.500
I highly recognize your ability,

19:39.620 --> 19:41.420
and I feel it's unfair to you too.

19:41.880 --> 19:43.560
But the way Xu Miyu does things

19:43.580 --> 19:45.390
is truly flawless.

19:45.890 --> 19:47.550
Besides, she has
the general manager's backing.

19:47.550 --> 19:48.700
What am I supposed to do?

19:48.700 --> 19:50.600
Then what do you want me to do?

19:50.630 --> 19:51.740
You make empty promises all day

19:51.740 --> 19:53.230
without giving anything practical.

19:53.230 --> 19:54.740
Should I even keep working here?

19:54.740 --> 19:56.480
Are you asking me
to fight a losing battle?

19:56.480 --> 19:58.630
If I can't survive here,
who will promote you?

19:58.630 --> 19:59.480
But I...

19:59.500 --> 20:01.360
Cut the crap and get out of the car.

20:03.200 --> 20:04.160
Get out!

20:26.750 --> 20:27.430
Wait.

20:27.450 --> 20:29.540
The height of that light is wrong.

20:29.900 --> 20:32.140
Move the whole chandelier up

20:32.170 --> 20:33.430
by about a meter, okay?

20:33.650 --> 20:35.230
Alright, let's step it up, everyone.

20:35.230 --> 20:35.880
Hurry up.

20:35.920 --> 20:36.510
Okay.

20:36.510 --> 20:37.400
Mr. Ji.

20:43.750 --> 20:44.560
Mr. Duan.

20:45.590 --> 20:46.850
The stage looks great.

20:47.040 --> 20:49.100
You really know how to spend my money.

20:50.330 --> 20:52.390
You have to spend money to make money.

20:52.610 --> 20:53.940
What's wrong, Mr. Duan?

20:54.370 --> 20:56.330
Why didn't you find a comfortable place

20:56.330 --> 20:57.660
instead of coming here?

20:57.990 --> 20:59.390
I'm on-site inspection.

20:59.830 --> 21:02.160
Did you think I was just pampered?

21:09.770 --> 21:11.430
The tableware doesn't match.

21:14.870 --> 21:15.920
The cooking is bad too.

21:15.920 --> 21:17.440
Brother, come help out.

21:17.510 --> 21:17.970
Hurry up and help.

21:17.970 --> 21:18.860
Waiter!

21:20.600 --> 21:21.430
Waiter!

21:24.230 --> 21:25.320
Waiter!

21:27.480 --> 21:29.210
The service is a total mess too.

21:29.360 --> 21:31.060
How can you expect me to trust you,

21:31.060 --> 21:31.780
Mr. Ji?

21:32.750 --> 21:33.480
Mr. Duan,

21:33.600 --> 21:36.500
you need to
trust your own investment vision.

21:36.530 --> 21:37.750
But when I invested,

21:37.750 --> 21:39.480
I didn't expect you would come.

21:41.460 --> 21:42.460
Surprise.

21:44.090 --> 21:45.790
Do you know what they said

21:45.790 --> 21:46.960
when the Jazz Bar project was approved

21:46.960 --> 21:47.790
by the board?

21:47.960 --> 21:48.960
What did they say?

21:49.200 --> 21:50.360
Flashy but impractical,

21:50.360 --> 21:51.640
with short-term effects.

21:51.640 --> 21:52.940
You worked your heart out

21:52.940 --> 21:54.310
for the whole hotel,

21:54.610 --> 21:56.610
but they don't appreciate it at all.

21:57.000 --> 21:59.060
I don't need anyone's appreciation.

21:59.360 --> 22:00.470
I'm just doing what

22:00.680 --> 22:02.710
a hotel general manager should do.

22:06.100 --> 22:07.050
Mr. Duan,

22:07.410 --> 22:09.410
when our jazz bar opens,

22:09.440 --> 22:11.700
do you want me
to save a few tables for you?

22:18.010 --> 22:18.900
Just this?

22:19.640 --> 22:21.920
I think you should forget about it.

22:27.380 --> 22:29.240
You are definitely going to lose.

22:30.070 --> 22:31.400
I will accept my defeat.

22:34.290 --> 22:35.050
Take care.

22:50.120 --> 22:51.950
Didn't you go see Duan Aoxiang?

22:52.150 --> 22:54.010
He invited you for afternoon tea?

23:01.160 --> 23:02.880
Duan Aoxiang is right.

23:03.330 --> 23:05.240
Before our jazz bar opens,

23:05.620 --> 23:07.220
we must get our refreshments

23:07.290 --> 23:08.320
sorted out quickly.

23:08.320 --> 23:10.120
And stop restocking

23:10.240 --> 23:11.240
that durian puff.

23:11.850 --> 23:12.400
Okay.

23:13.400 --> 23:14.510
By the way,

23:14.750 --> 23:16.580
you and this VIP Chun
have been interacting a lot

23:16.580 --> 23:17.520
and chatting quite happily.

23:17.520 --> 23:19.680
She called again
to ask about your schedule.

23:19.680 --> 23:21.000
What VIP Chun?

23:23.900 --> 23:27.470
[Jiang Zhichun]

23:26.430 --> 23:27.750
I have a new idea.

23:27.770 --> 23:29.740
Let's have dinner tonight and talk.

23:29.740 --> 23:30.670
I'll pick you up.

23:30.800 --> 23:31.800
Stop pretending.

23:32.890 --> 23:34.240
I have a feeling

23:34.360 --> 23:35.540
that she may not necessarily

23:35.540 --> 23:37.540
be coming for our Purong Hotel.

23:37.960 --> 23:39.170
Dianjiangchun is indeed

23:39.170 --> 23:41.050
a valued patron of our Purong Hotel.

23:41.050 --> 23:42.580
No matter what she's after,

23:43.160 --> 23:45.020
as long as it's a win-win situation,

23:45.020 --> 23:46.700
we should do our best to cooperate.

23:46.700 --> 23:48.610
What if she takes advantage of work

23:48.610 --> 23:50.610
to talk to you about something else?

23:52.770 --> 23:53.920
Outside of work,

23:54.730 --> 23:55.530
we

23:56.420 --> 23:58.220
have nothing else to talk about.

23:58.270 --> 23:59.070
Junior,

24:00.280 --> 24:02.310
do you have someone in your heart?

24:05.770 --> 24:06.480
Right?

24:10.250 --> 24:11.880
Does she know?

24:42.530 --> 24:43.240
Ms. Xu.

24:43.710 --> 24:44.780
Ms. Jiang.

24:44.930 --> 24:46.580
Are you here to check in?

24:46.610 --> 24:48.070
No, I have an appointment.

24:48.200 --> 24:49.450
I bought you some milk tea.

24:49.450 --> 24:50.870
Oh, how can I accept this?

24:51.020 --> 24:52.620
It's a perk for my followers.

24:52.950 --> 24:53.800
Take it.

24:53.830 --> 24:54.630
Thank you.

24:54.650 --> 24:55.550
Don't mention it.

24:55.550 --> 24:57.410
We'll be seeing each other often.

24:58.210 --> 24:58.810
By the way,

24:58.920 --> 25:01.680
why do you think milk tea

25:01.710 --> 25:03.560
is so appealing to young people?

25:04.600 --> 25:06.660
Sorry, it's an occupational hazard.

25:06.690 --> 25:08.310
A few milk tea shops

25:08.340 --> 25:09.850
have been talking to me
about partnerships lately.

25:09.850 --> 25:11.530
For someone

25:11.550 --> 25:13.150
at my age,

25:13.180 --> 25:14.400
I really can't tell the difference

25:14.400 --> 25:16.710
between the different brands.

25:17.450 --> 25:19.250
How do you think I should choose?

25:20.290 --> 25:21.570
Could it be because

25:21.590 --> 25:24.270
milk tea conveys
goodwill better than water?

25:24.350 --> 25:25.500
Not only is it sweet,

25:25.550 --> 25:26.870
but it's also versatile.

25:26.870 --> 25:28.040
You can add anything to it.

25:28.040 --> 25:29.170
It rejects nothing,

25:29.240 --> 25:30.990
which makes it a very easygoing drink.

25:30.990 --> 25:33.030
That's a good angle.

25:36.010 --> 25:36.970
My appointment is here.

25:36.970 --> 25:37.850
I'll get going.

25:37.870 --> 25:38.690
Thank you.

25:40.140 --> 25:40.870
Ji Feng.

25:42.030 --> 25:43.680
Let's find a place to talk.

25:43.720 --> 25:44.880
Let's go. My car is outside.

25:44.880 --> 25:45.740
Did you drive here?

25:45.740 --> 25:46.440
Then I'll ride with you.

25:46.440 --> 25:46.680
Let's go.

25:46.680 --> 25:47.200
Okay.

26:22.620 --> 26:24.010
I'll show you something.

26:24.010 --> 26:24.690
Okay.

26:33.460 --> 26:35.060
You've published a new book?

26:35.220 --> 26:36.090
Take a look. What do you think?

26:35.970 --> 26:36.720
[Chun's Daily Taste]

26:38.750 --> 26:39.930
[Chun's Daily Taste]

26:39.300 --> 26:39.990
It's great.

26:40.210 --> 26:41.610
The photos are very good.

26:42.130 --> 26:43.850
This is my first time publishing a book.

26:43.850 --> 26:46.650
It records my travels, shop explorations,

26:46.680 --> 26:48.090
and some food notes.

26:48.390 --> 26:49.450
Congratulations.

26:49.670 --> 26:50.270
Thank you.

26:53.980 --> 26:55.100
Recently, our team

26:55.120 --> 26:56.950
is also choosing a venue

26:56.980 --> 26:58.820
for the new book's signing event.

26:58.820 --> 27:00.370
We are dazzled by the choices,

27:00.370 --> 27:02.960
and the more we look,
the less satisfied we become.

27:02.960 --> 27:04.090
So,

27:05.360 --> 27:07.300
could I hold the signing event

27:07.580 --> 27:09.180
for my new book at your hotel?

27:11.900 --> 27:12.580
Of course.

27:12.610 --> 27:14.850
If it's not too much trouble.

27:15.430 --> 27:17.950
Of course. It would be our pleasure.

27:18.180 --> 27:18.850
Okay.

27:23.860 --> 27:26.120
Hello, I've decided.

27:26.440 --> 27:28.740
The book signing will be at Purong.

27:29.490 --> 27:30.820
Eliminate the others.

27:33.260 --> 27:35.570
Can I check out the venue next week?

27:36.200 --> 27:37.860
I'll be at your full disposal.

27:38.730 --> 27:39.120
Okay.

27:39.310 --> 27:40.760
Hello, your fish is ready.

27:40.760 --> 27:41.440
Enjoy your meal.

27:41.440 --> 27:42.200
Thank you.

27:42.740 --> 27:43.930
Try their fish.

27:43.960 --> 27:44.890
It's delicious.

27:45.130 --> 27:45.680
Okay.

27:50.820 --> 27:52.020
The fish is so tender.

27:52.920 --> 27:54.250
It really is delicious.

28:01.400 --> 28:03.000
It really is Dianjiangchun!

28:03.080 --> 28:03.610
Let's go.

28:04.910 --> 28:06.320
We really like you.

28:06.600 --> 28:08.800
Hello. I really like your videos.

28:08.820 --> 28:10.480
Can we take a picture with you?

28:10.540 --> 28:11.100
Sure.

28:12.000 --> 28:13.590
Sir, could you take a picture for us?

28:13.590 --> 28:14.310
Thank you.

28:15.680 --> 28:16.330
Okay.

28:17.180 --> 28:18.100
Okay.

28:18.130 --> 28:19.530
One, two, three.

28:20.240 --> 28:20.990
-It should be
-Thank you.

28:20.990 --> 28:21.800
fine.

28:21.840 --> 28:24.130
Are you that general manager
of Purong Hotel

28:24.130 --> 28:26.000
who plays the saxophone?

28:26.020 --> 28:27.760
I've seen you in a video.

28:27.920 --> 28:28.270
Hello.

28:28.270 --> 28:29.480
Really?

28:29.500 --> 28:32.010
Are you two dating?

28:32.850 --> 28:34.080
You misunderstood.

28:35.210 --> 28:37.140
Can I take a picture with you alone?

28:37.170 --> 28:38.450
Me too!

28:38.480 --> 28:41.210
-I'll take one later.
-I need to use the bathroom.

28:43.720 --> 28:44.510
Thank you.

28:44.510 --> 28:45.480
My turn!

28:51.610 --> 28:55.470
[Mei Restaurant]

28:53.840 --> 28:54.630
How is it?

28:54.650 --> 28:56.780
Their food tastes pretty good, right?

28:57.050 --> 28:58.380
It's really delicious.

28:58.860 --> 28:59.800
It's not easy.

29:00.160 --> 29:02.060
Our tastes finally align.

29:11.530 --> 29:12.980
You don't need to see me off.
I'll take a taxi back.

29:12.980 --> 29:13.890
Why?

29:17.770 --> 29:20.090
You're a public figure.

29:23.190 --> 29:25.650
Why do you have more
of an idol burden than me?

29:26.500 --> 29:27.800
I'm just kidding.

29:28.090 --> 29:30.040
You don't work in the internet ecosystem.

29:30.040 --> 29:32.360
So you don't understand
my work environment.

29:32.360 --> 29:33.560
Let's talk in the car.

29:33.770 --> 29:35.920
I promise you won't affect
my public image.

29:35.920 --> 29:36.810
Let's go.

29:36.840 --> 29:37.600
Okay.

29:56.390 --> 29:58.170
We created this Dianjiangchun persona

29:58.170 --> 30:00.500
in a way that naturally invites shipping—

30:01.290 --> 30:03.000
she's single, beautiful,

30:03.360 --> 30:05.120
tasteful, and romantic.

30:05.680 --> 30:08.040
Almost any male guest around my age

30:09.050 --> 30:10.050
with decent looks

30:10.160 --> 30:11.450
who shows up on my livestream

30:11.450 --> 30:14.850
ends up being pushed by the audience
as my rumored boyfriend.

30:14.960 --> 30:16.000
But,

30:16.030 --> 30:18.720
this does nothing but good for my traffic.

30:18.880 --> 30:21.010
The other side of traffic is scandals,

30:23.040 --> 30:24.040
you know?

30:24.480 --> 30:26.940
Being my rumored boyfriend
is not a bad deal.

30:27.030 --> 30:28.880
They've all become popular.

30:28.900 --> 30:30.070
I am very valuable.

30:32.390 --> 30:33.320
Thank you.

30:34.110 --> 30:36.920
Thank you for being willing to
help Purong Hotel.

30:39.030 --> 30:40.110
Is that all?

30:44.130 --> 30:45.610
I've arrived.

31:02.750 --> 31:03.440
Thank you.

31:03.560 --> 31:04.270
Bye.

31:08.370 --> 31:09.130
Ji Feng!

31:10.890 --> 31:12.420
When will we meet next time?

31:13.900 --> 31:15.730
I'll ask the PR department

31:15.760 --> 31:17.300
to contact your team for
your signing event.

31:17.300 --> 31:18.100
What about me?

31:20.060 --> 31:20.630
What?

31:21.090 --> 31:22.300
Can't I ask you out?

31:29.860 --> 31:31.060
Keep in touch on WeChat.

31:31.060 --> 31:31.820
I'm leaving.

31:32.050 --> 31:32.920
Bye.

31:45.970 --> 31:46.930
I'm off work.

31:47.020 --> 31:47.650
Bye.

31:47.680 --> 31:48.560
Bye.

31:49.040 --> 31:49.830
Bye.

32:31.190 --> 32:35.030
♪ Love is truly not easy to obtain ♪

32:38.570 --> 32:42.270
♪ I can't hold on to you
even if you want to leave ♪

32:45.540 --> 32:49.670
♪ I tell myself I'm not hurt
once things settle down ♪

32:53.180 --> 32:56.990
♪ but I realize I can't deceive myself ♪

33:00.560 --> 33:04.460
♪ I always say life is already
hard enough ♪

33:08.200 --> 33:12.230
♪ so what else is there worth trying for ♪

33:15.540 --> 33:19.580
♪ Friends comfort me,
telling me to have a drink ♪

33:23.140 --> 33:26.890
♪ But I've already started living
like I'm not myself anymore ♪

33:34.560 --> 33:38.240
Dianjiangchun's team will come to
the hotel to check the venue tomorrow.

33:38.240 --> 33:39.680
We must treat them

33:39.010 --> 33:45.340
[Purong Hotel]

33:39.680 --> 33:41.680
with the highest standard for VIPs.

33:41.830 --> 33:43.590
We must provide the service
that best reflects

33:43.590 --> 33:45.640
the style of Purong Hotel.

33:45.950 --> 33:46.920
No department

33:46.950 --> 33:48.430
can take chances.

33:48.820 --> 33:49.680
Any negligence

33:50.000 --> 33:52.160
will be strictly punished

33:52.160 --> 33:54.330
according to
the hotel's management rules.

33:54.330 --> 33:55.290
Director Li,

33:55.050 --> 33:56.270
[Purong Hotel]

33:55.310 --> 33:57.670
make an interview flowchart for me

33:57.700 --> 33:59.030
and send it to the work group.

33:59.030 --> 33:59.990
Okay, Mr. Ji.

34:00.140 --> 34:01.920
Who's in charge of your department?

34:01.920 --> 34:03.590
Is it still Lu Zhenzhen?

34:04.640 --> 34:07.490
She was rejected
right after I submitted the list.

34:07.550 --> 34:09.020
It seems our Mr. Ji

34:09.040 --> 34:10.560
isn't interested in her.

34:10.580 --> 34:12.449
This place needs to be decorated
more exquisitely.

34:12.449 --> 34:14.190
Let me know if you
have any questions later.

34:14.190 --> 34:16.150
No more kissing up to the new boss.

34:16.400 --> 34:17.199
Just wait.

34:17.440 --> 34:19.710
She'll come back to kiss up to you.

34:23.949 --> 34:24.840
Come in.

34:27.110 --> 34:27.920
Mr. Ji,

34:29.400 --> 34:30.460
you asked for me?

34:30.929 --> 34:31.699
Yes.

34:33.370 --> 34:35.969
I've already informed
the other departments.

34:36.040 --> 34:38.330
Our hotel will soon host

34:38.360 --> 34:40.820
a new book signing event
for Dianjiangchun.

34:41.070 --> 34:42.280
I want you to

34:42.840 --> 34:44.300
follow up on this project.

34:44.580 --> 34:45.590
Okay, Mr. Ji.

34:47.580 --> 34:48.679
This is her new book.

34:48.679 --> 34:50.080
Take it back and study it.

34:52.120 --> 34:53.120
I see.

34:55.310 --> 34:56.260
[Chun's Daily Taste]

34:56.659 --> 34:59.230
Mr. Ji, did you meet Ms. Jiang before?

35:05.110 --> 35:06.510
Sorry, I asked too much.

35:06.530 --> 35:07.370
We were

35:08.860 --> 35:10.060
college classmates.

35:16.550 --> 35:19.230
I'll go back
and study this book carefully.

35:19.410 --> 35:20.340
Don't worry.

35:32.490 --> 35:34.370
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

35:38.160 --> 35:40.650
She is indeed a top blogger
with 10 million followers.

35:40.650 --> 35:42.790
Her book is like a pictorial.

35:43.330 --> 35:45.790
I'm starting to understand
why you like her.

35:46.000 --> 35:47.850
So, we need to do a good job

35:47.880 --> 35:49.430
with this book signing event.

35:49.430 --> 35:50.630
We can't let her down

35:50.650 --> 35:52.380
for trusting our Purong Hotel.

35:56.800 --> 35:58.230
You're about to work

35:58.230 --> 35:59.650
with your favorite blogger.

35:59.650 --> 36:01.650
Why don't you look excited at all?

36:02.030 --> 36:03.280
Of course I'm excited.

36:03.280 --> 36:04.510
I am excited.

36:04.710 --> 36:05.760
Are you?

36:05.860 --> 36:08.390
You look like you have something
on your mind.

36:08.660 --> 36:10.460
I don't have anything on my mind.

36:11.230 --> 36:12.440
That's good.

36:13.560 --> 36:14.470
Then I won't bother you anymore.

36:14.470 --> 36:16.070
I'll go make you some supper.

36:17.030 --> 36:18.230
Thank you, Qi.

36:26.120 --> 36:29.110
[With old friends, let the past rest;
brew new tea, and begin again.]

36:29.140 --> 36:30.910
[Let poetry and wine carry us
through our youth—Chun]

36:41.440 --> 36:42.290
We were

36:43.050 --> 36:44.340
college classmates.

36:48.200 --> 36:49.450
[With old friends, let the past rest;
brew new tea, and begin again.]

36:49.480 --> 36:50.850
[Let poetry and wine carry us
through our youth—Chun]

36:53.820 --> 36:55.570
[Chun's Daily Taste]

37:06.640 --> 37:10.210
[Always on the road
recording the flavors of the mortal world]

37:10.230 --> 37:17.700
[Dianjiangchun – "Chun's Daily Taste"
New Book Sharing Event]

37:26.030 --> 37:27.000
Ahead is

37:27.020 --> 37:29.420
the multi-function hall prepared for you.

37:36.680 --> 37:37.540
This way, please.

37:36.730 --> 37:38.200
[Dianjiangchun –
New Book Sharing Signing Event]

37:50.990 --> 37:54.870
[Dianjiangchun –
New Book Sharing Signing Event]

37:52.300 --> 37:53.190
Let me.

37:53.220 --> 37:54.930
This is the main venue.

37:59.220 --> 38:00.000
[Dianjiangchun –
New Book Sharing Signing Event]

38:08.880 --> 38:09.900
[Always on the road
recording the flavors of the mortal world]

38:09.930 --> 38:11.290
[Dianjiangchun – "Chun's Daily Taste"
New Book Sharing Event]

38:12.960 --> 38:14.040
It's so beautiful.

38:14.400 --> 38:15.340
I really like it.

38:15.230 --> 38:16.310
[Dianjiangchun –
New Book Sharing Signing Event]

38:15.710 --> 38:16.920
Thank you, Ji Feng.

38:23.970 --> 38:25.050
Let's

38:26.000 --> 38:27.310
take a look up ahead.

38:30.420 --> 38:33.060
We chose to use blue and white

38:33.360 --> 38:34.010
because...

38:34.010 --> 38:34.720
Director Bai,

38:34.720 --> 38:36.370
there's a situation
at the banquet hall entrance.

38:36.370 --> 38:37.640
Ms. Xu, go take a look.

38:37.670 --> 38:38.070
Okay.

38:40.770 --> 38:41.970
So many people today.

38:44.780 --> 38:47.510
[Always on the road
recording the flavors of the mortal world]

38:46.730 --> 38:47.290
Miss,

38:47.320 --> 38:48.760
when will the signing start?

38:47.530 --> 38:49.260
[Dianjiangchun – "Chun's Daily Taste"
New Book Sharing Event]

38:48.800 --> 38:49.400
Miss,

38:49.400 --> 38:50.440
when will it start?

38:50.440 --> 38:51.280
Excuse me.

38:51.280 --> 38:52.880
It will start exactly at two o'clock.

38:52.880 --> 38:54.760
Please wait a moment.

38:54.780 --> 38:56.580
Everyone, please wait outside.

38:58.410 --> 39:00.160
Ms. Jiang Zhichun has already arrived.

39:00.160 --> 39:02.310
Once it starts, everyone
will have a chance to see her.

39:02.310 --> 39:03.840
Please be patient for now, okay?

39:03.840 --> 39:04.030
Okay.

39:04.030 --> 39:04.920
Just a moment.

39:04.920 --> 39:06.480
Calm down.

39:06.670 --> 39:08.870
-Where is your director?
-I don't know.

39:09.330 --> 39:10.390
Security Department.

39:10.390 --> 39:11.860
We need help at the banquet hall.

39:11.860 --> 39:13.790
Can you send some more people over?

39:16.150 --> 39:17.130
Don't worry!

39:17.150 --> 39:18.190
I know.

39:18.190 --> 39:19.110
Please wait a moment, everyone.

39:19.110 --> 39:20.230
You'll all get a chance to see her.

39:20.230 --> 39:21.230
Just a moment.

39:21.050 --> 39:22.390
[Always on the road
recording the flavors of the mortal world]

39:22.420 --> 39:23.770
[Dianjiangchun – "Chun's Daily Taste"
New Book Sharing Event]

39:38.680 --> 39:40.210
Why didn't you ask for help?

39:40.370 --> 39:41.290
-Come on.
-It's OK.

39:41.290 --> 39:42.420
Give this to me.

39:44.450 --> 39:45.450
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

39:46.270 --> 39:48.550
How are the preparations
for the upcoming talk?

39:48.550 --> 39:50.320
The wiring is all set in the venue.

39:50.320 --> 39:51.980
The cold buffet is being prepared.

39:51.980 --> 39:53.500
As for the guest speaker,

39:53.550 --> 39:55.000
I will personally be responsible

39:55.000 --> 39:56.380
for bringing him to the banquet.

39:56.380 --> 39:57.570
Don't worry.

40:04.550 --> 40:05.230
Thank you.

40:05.390 --> 40:06.790
[Banquet Hall]

40:08.330 --> 40:08.890
Wait.

40:16.810 --> 40:17.650
Your foot.

40:20.810 --> 40:21.600
Thank you.

40:21.630 --> 40:22.510
Let me help.

40:24.590 --> 40:25.440
Lift it up.

40:25.970 --> 40:26.880
[Banquet Hall]

40:26.670 --> 40:27.540
Hold me.
